<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV14">
<l>tūymaiyōka māyiṉāytu ḻāyalaṅkal mālaiyā</l>
<l>yāmaiyāki yāḻkaṭaṟṟu yiṉṟavāti tēvaniṉ</l>
<l>nāmatēya miṉṉateṉṉa vallamalla mākiluñ</l>
<l>cāmavēta kītaṉāya cakrapāṇi yallaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O You who are pure consciousness! O You with a garland of tulasi shoots!</l>
<l>O Primordial God who slept in the deep ocean, becoming a tortoise!</l>
<l>Even though we are not capable of saying these are Your names,</l>
<l>are You not the Discus-Holder sung about in the Sāma-veda?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
